Player 1 > Commands:
 - insert <ROW> <COLUMN> <H/V> <WORD>
    <H/V> stands for H: horizontal, V: vertical.

 - help
    Prints this help text.

 - quit
    Terminates the game.

 - save
    Saves the game to the current config file.

 - load <CONFIGFILE>
    load config file and start game.
